messages.title: It's LIB DEM or LABOUR HERE!
messages.content: Only the Liberal Democrats can end 40 years of Labour rule of Haringey Council. Bookmakers have put the Conservatives as the 100 to 1 outsiders in the race locally.

mentions.tacticalSituation: The Conservatives will finish at least 10,000 votes behind Lib Dem Lynne Featherstone.

images.caption: The Conservative election record in Hornsey & Wood Green is consistently 3rd or 4th place, with the Liberal Democrats and Labour in the lead.

leaflet.additionalNotes: Promoted by Park Communications. Printed by Park Communications.
